description:
We are only a few weeks away from the NBA play-in tournament. On this weeks WHAT'S BURNIN', Matt and Stak break down the playoff picture and discuss the biggest matchups of the week. Plus, they talk DeMarcus Cousin, Iverson Classic & answer your fan questions.
